extracted_text: C1(P) Planned Local Business District. This district is designed to cater to the ordinary shopping needs of the immediate neighborhood with emphasis on convenience goods. This district is customarily located adjacent to an arterial street and generally surrounded by residential areas. To promote the essential design features with the C1(P) district, plan approval is a requirement.
llm_output.rationale: The input provides information about the C1(P) Planned Local Business District, including its purpose and location. The dimensional requirements table on page 146 shows the minimum lot size for this district.
